    <div class="card">
        <h2>Machine presets</h2>
        <p>Good Razor candidate: weld presets, weave visualization, speeddata/zonedata editors, and CDB file management.</p>
        <p class="muted">Keep heavy parsing services outside the page model.</p>
    </div>
</div>
